- SwankyNoob Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy describes how SwankyNoob collects, uses, stores and protects personal information when you use our programs, projects and websites. By using our services, you agree to the collection and use of your personal information in accordance with this policy.

✓ Information Collection
1.1 We collect personal information only when voluntarily provided by you, such as in the case of account registration or contact form submission. The information we may collect includes name, email address, contact information, and other information necessary to provide our services.

✓ Use of Information
2.1 We use the personal information collected for the following purposes:

To provide and improve our programs, projects and websites.
Managing your account and providing customer support.
To personalize your experience and send you relevant information about our services.
To comply with legal and regulatory requirements.
Information Storage
3.1 We keep your personal information on our secure systems and take reasonable steps to ensure data security. However, no data transmission over the Internet or storage system is completely secure, so we cannot guarantee the absolute security of information.

✓ Sharing of Information
4.1 We do not share your personal information with third parties except in the following circumstances:

When we have your explicit permission.
When necessary to comply with legal obligations.
To protect our rights, property or safety, or that of other users.
Cookies
5.1 Our websites may use cookies to improve the user experience. Cookies are small files that are stored on your device and help us analyze traffic patterns and personalize content. You can choose to disable cookies in your browser settings, but this may affect the functionality of our services.

✓ Indicative Rating
6.1 Some of our programs are rated and may require additional information to verify the age of users. This information will be collected only to comply with legal obligations and will be used solely for this purpose.

